"""
        Test that the equality operator returns False when comparing two
        Locate request payloads with different object group member.
        """
a = payloads.LocateRequestPayload(object_group_member=enums.
    ObjectGroupMember.GROUP_MEMBER_DEFAULT)
b = payloads.LocateRequestPayload(object_group_member=enums.
    ObjectGroupMember.GROUP_MEMBER_FRESH)
self.assertFalse(a == b)
self.assertFalse(b == a)
